# MERN Auth & Profile App

This is a full-stack MERN application that includes 
**user registration, login (JWT-based)**, **protected routes**, and **profile updates with image upload** using Multer. 
The frontend is built with **React + Vite** and connects to an **Express + MongoDB backend**.

---

## ðŸ”§ Tech Stack

### Backend
- Node.js + Express
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- JWT (Authentication)
- Bcrypt.js (Password Hashing)
- Multer (Image Upload)

### Frontend
- React (Vite)
- Axios
- React Router DOM
- LocalStorage for JWT

